      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the iconic S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in peak operational status. The chassis is structurally immaculate with a reinforced rear subframe and original factory bushings, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential with zero mechanical lash. Flawlessly maintained and free of any oxidation or wear, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
